PN,40501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FA "cowardly" teenager who went on the
OL,7,Frun for two years after being involved
OL,8,Fin the ambush, robbery and fatal
OL,9,Fstabbing of a man has been jailed.
OL,11,FYoung father Michael Afonso Peixoto,
OL,12,F27, was lured into a trap by a gang of
OL,13,Frobbers and killed in Thornton Heath,
OL,14,Fsouth London, on December 19 2023.
OL,16,FThe five robbers, wearing face masks,
OL,17,Fhad travelled to the scene in a stolen
OL,18,FBMW and confronted the victim, who had
OL,19,Fgone there with a female friend in a
OL,20,FVauxhall Grandland.
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FMr Peixoto was chased, cornered and
OL,7,Ffatally stabbed while his friend was
OL,8,Fforced out of the car at knifepoint.
OL,10,FOne of the robbers, Ali Abdul Basit,
OL,11,Fwho was aged 17, fled the country and
OL,12,Ftravelled to Dubai, Egypt and Pakistan
OL,13,Fbefore returning to the UK on May 3
OL,14,Flast year when he was arrested.
OL,16,FForensic evidence matched Basit's DNA
OL,17,Fto a cigarette butt discarded at the
OL,18,Fscene and he was found guilty of
OL,19,Fmanslaughter and robbery following a
OL,20,Fthree-week trial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FOn Friday, Basit, now aged 19, from
OL,7,FMerton, south London, was jailed at
OL,8,Fthe Old Bailey for eight years and six
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FSentencing, Judge Rosa Dean condemned
OL,12,Fthe "shocking level of violence" used
OL,13,Fby the gang who were intent on taking
OL,14,FMr Peixoto's car and finding drugs in
OL,15,Fa "planned robbery".
OL,17,FBeforehand, Basit had helped the
OL,18,Fgetaway driver by arranging for false
OL,19,Fnumber plates to go on the stolen BMW.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@`O]wD@COUwD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FJudge Dean said: "Your victim was
OL,7,Fdrawn into a trap in Mayfield Crescent.
OL,9,F"He thought he was going to be selling
OL,10,Fdrugs.
OL,12,F"As soon as he got out of the car you,
OL,13,Fall wearing face masks, swarmed over
OL,14,Fto the car.
OL,16,F"The victim was unarmed and he ran for
OL,17,Fit but was chased down."
OL,19,FBasit got into the Vauxhall and held
OL,20,Fout a knife to his female friend, who
OL,21,Fwas forced out of the car, she said.
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FThe judge went on: "Michael had been
OL,7,Fcornered and killed in a nearby
OL,8,Fdriveway.
OL,10,F"He had a number of stab wounds
OL,11,Fincluding one directly into the heart."
OL,13,FShe dismissed the defendant's account
OL,14,Fto jurors in his trial as
OL,15,F"ridiculous", saying he had made the
OL,16,Ffoolish mistake of trying to be clever.
OL,18,FThree other robbers were tried and
OL,19,Fsentenced in 2024, with Basit only
OL,20,Freturning to the UK afterwards.
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUsD@gO]wD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FJudge Dean told him: "Your cowardly
OL,7,Fdecision to flee meant Michael's
OL,8,Ffamily had to endure a second trial."
OL,10,FFollowing the earlier trial, Zak
OL,11,FBaako, 30, from Croydon, south London,
OL,12,Fwas found guilty of murder and jailed
OL,13,Ffor life with a minimum term of 28
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FJohn Budal, 22, from Thornton Heath,
OL,17,Fwas found guilty of manslaughter and
OL,18,Frobbery and Omari Peat, 25 of Mitcham,
OL,19,Fwas found guilty of robbery.
OL,26,@nD@VOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FA fifth male remains at large who
OL,7,FBasit has refused to identify, telling
OL,8,Fjurors in his trial he was not a
OL,9,F"snitch".
OL,11,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,12,Fthe court, niece Jessica described Mr
OL,13,FPeixoto as a "bubbly and funny
OL,14,Fperson", "larger than life" and a
OL,15,Ffather to "the most amazing boy".
OL,17,FShe said the family had endured her
OL,18,Funcle being "reduced to a drug
OL,19,Fdealer", saying he was "so much more
OL,20,Fthan that".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@HO]uD@NOUvD@GO]vD@JOUvD@[O]wD@
OL,26,AKOUwD@`O]zD@MOU{D@GO]{D@XOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,F"He was larger than life, full of joy
OL,7,Fand humour. He had hopes, dreams and a
OL,8,Ffuture that you stole from him, from
OL,9,Fus," she told the defendant.
OL,11,FSister Maria told Basit in her
OL,12,Fstatement: "We lost a person who was
OL,13,Fkind and full of life. I hope you find
OL,14,Fforgiveness but Michael's family will
OL,15,Fnever forgive you."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@DO]tD@LOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Martin Thorpe,
OL,7,Ffrom Scotland Yard, said: "After
OL,8,FMichael's violent murder, Basit
OL,9,Fimmediately left the country and
OL,10,Ftravelled to Dubai via Venice then
OL,11,FEgypt, eventually arriving in Pakistan
OL,12,Fwhere he remained for months.
OL,14,F"Basit returned to the UK after the
OL,15,Fconviction of three other men in
OL,16,Fconnection with Michael's death,
OL,17,Fpossibly on the false pretence that he
OL,18,Fhas got away with his actions.
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,F"What Basit didn't know is that our
OL,7,Fofficers had compiled an extensive
OL,8,Famount of evidence, including phone
OL,9,Fdata which linked him to the other
OL,10,Fthree convicted men at the time of the
OL,11,Fassault.
OL,13,F"After he was arrested, our officers
OL,14,Fwere able to get his DNA from an
OL,15,Fasthma inhaler at his house which
OL,16,Fmatched DNA found on a cigarette butt
OL,17,Fat the scene.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779879767
OL,3,C'Cowardly' teenager jailed over
OL,4,Cambush, stabbing and robbery
OL,6,F"This case emphasises the Met's
OL,7,Fpersistent pursual for justice in
OL,8,Fmaking sure that anyone who carries
OL,9,Fout such violent actions is held
OL,10,Faccountable."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/11
